TEACHING PROGRAM
Covers survival skills, all 5 swim strokes, advanced skills/techniques or skills required in a lifeguard certification ONLY.
Prerequisite : You must exceed the water surface in the pool.

RM500 per 4 lessons for the whole group.
1 complimentary Trial lesson! RM20 refundable deposit required.
60 minutes length.
6 weeks validity.
At your desired pool or we suggested you go to.
 

SQUAD PROGRAM
Programmed training for open water, competition, or lifeguard swimmers.
Prerequisite : Must be able to swim at least 100 meters.

RM250 per person for 16 "Attend or Forfeit" lessons.
Minimum of 5 to start the class (Please invite 4 others).
1 complimentary Trial lesson! RM20/pax refundable deposit required.
60 minutes length.
4 weeks validity.
At your desired pool or we suggested you go to.
 

